OL,3,CFormer Mayor of Wolverhampton resigns
OL,4,Cfrom the Labour Party
OL,6,FThe former Mayor of Wolverhampton has
OL,7,Fannounced her resignation from the
OL,8,FLabour Party.
OL,10,FIn an open letter addressed to Labour
OL,11,FParty leader Keir Starmer, Councillor
OL,12,FClaire Darke, who is a long-serving
OL,13,FLabour representative for Park Ward,
OL,14,Fexpressed her profound disillusionment
OL,15,Fwith the current direction of the
OL,16,Fparty under Starmer's leadership.
