OL,3,CFormer Mayor of Wolverhampton resigns
OL,4,Cfrom the Labour Party
OL,6,FWith the General Election just weeks
OL,7,Faway, Councillor Drake accuses the
OL,8,FLabour Party of straying from its core
OL,9,Fvalues, becoming increasingly
OL,10,Fautocratic, and marginalising diverse
OL,11,Fvoices, particularly those of women,
OL,12,Fpeople of colour, Muslims, and Jews.
OL,14,FShe writes: "The Labour Party has
OL,15,Fstrayed from the core values I once
OL,16,Fshared with the Party.
OL,18,F"My political beliefs prevent me from
OL,19,Fcompromising my principles for a party
OL,20,Fthat appears to have none.
