OL,3,CFormer Mayor of Wolverhampton resigns
OL,4,Cfrom the Labour Party
OL,6,F"The democratic fabric of the Labour
OL,7,FParty has been compromised under your
OL,8,Fleadership, Keir Starmer, becoming
OL,9,Fincreasingly autocratic that
OL,10,Fmarginalises diverse voices,
OL,11,Fespecially those of women, people of
OL,12,Fcolour, Muslims, and Jews.
OL,14,F"This betrayal of democratic ideals,
OL,15,Falong with the party's major shift
OL,16,Ftowards antisemitism and islamophobia,
OL,17,Fis unacceptable."
