OL,3,CFormer Mayor of Wolverhampton resigns
OL,4,Cfrom the Labour Party
OL,6,FIn response to Claire Darke's open
OL,7,Fletter , a Labour spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Keir Starmer has changed the Labour
OL,9,Fparty into one which is proudly
OL,10,Fcountry first, party second - with a
OL,11,Fmanifesto for change.
OL,13,F"If we are privileged enough to be
OL,14,Felected, then Labour will be returning
OL,15,Fthe government to the service of
OL,16,Fworking people."
